00:24:46,136 --> 00:24:51,066
They saw that he was a king,
and he was a king of a nation


511
00:24:51,066 --> 00:24:53,186
that was the world's
most technologically


512
00:24:53,186 --> 00:24:54,706
advanced country.


513
00:24:55,626 --> 00:24:58,766
And so again, I think the
creators, this time Stan Lee


514
00:24:58,766 --> 00:25:00,466
and Jack Kirby, were
making a statement.


515
00:25:01,346 --> 00:25:05,206
Were making a statement just in
the choices they were making.


516
00:25:05,726 --> 00:25:09,596
And people loved Black
Panther right away.


517
00:25:09,596 --> 00:25:13,956
And they were very smart in
the stories they told with him,


518
00:25:13,956 --> 00:25:17,356
and I think they told some
very symbolic stories,


519
00:25:17,356 --> 00:25:18,716
like this next cover.


520
00:25:19,286 --> 00:25:21,946
So, here we are in
the 70s, and yeah,


