00:28:05,586 --> 00:28:07,006
like you are not evil.


572
00:28:07,276 --> 00:28:08,866
That people like you are good.


573
00:28:09,096 --> 00:28:12,356
And we can all work together
to create a better world.


574
00:28:12,656 --> 00:28:14,506
So, can you guess
my next friend?


575
00:28:15,226 --> 00:28:17,516
Storm! Storm, a mutant.


576
00:28:17,516 --> 00:28:20,746
In the Marvel universe we
kind of divide the characters


