00:29:07,506 --> 00:29:09,236
And it's a great message.


597
00:29:09,446 --> 00:29:11,266
And another message
was sent by this cover.


598
00:29:12,296 --> 00:29:14,336
I've mentioned America a
lot in this discussion.


