00:29:52,796 --> 00:29:53,896
and anywhere near Russia was,


612
00:29:54,116 --> 00:29:56,156
you know those were
commies, they're evil.


613
00:29:56,156 --> 00:29:59,806
But in the comics I saw that,
no, Russians can be good.


614
00:29:59,866 --> 00:30:01,036
Colossus is a hero.


615
00:30:01,086 --> 00:30:02,586
It meant a lot to me.


616
00:30:02,956 --> 00:30:06,136
So, also you see Nightcrawler,
with the blue face, he's German.


617
00:30:06,376 --> 00:30:09,126
Wolverine, with the
claws, from Canada.


618
00:30:10,906 --> 00:30:11,566
True story.


619
00:30:13,286 --> 00:30:14,066
International group.


620
00:30:14,406 --> 00:30:18,326
Again, I think they were making
a choice deliberately to say,


621
00:30:18,436 --> 00:30:20,406
again, it doesn't
matter who you are


622
00:30:20,406 --> 00:30:23,876
or where you come from,
we can all be heroes.


623
00:30:23,956 --> 00:30:24,816
We can all be heroes.


624
00:30:25,066 --> 00:30:26,316
And storm was really unique


625
00:30:26,316 --> 00:30:29,466
because she wasn't only
just really powerful,


626
00:30:29,686 --> 00:30:31,936
she can control the weather,
she can make it thunder


627
00:30:31,936 --> 00:30:33,056
and lightning and storm.


628
00:30:33,446 --> 00:30:37,316
Not only that, but she had
real strength of character.


629
00:30:37,316 --> 00:30:38,436
I mean look at this next cover.


630
00:30:38,966 --> 00:30:41,046
That's her rocking
the Grace Jones look,


631
00:30:41,076 --> 00:30:43,226
with the mohawk and the leather.


632
00:30:43,476 --> 00:30:45,096
And she was saying to the
world, hey this is me.


633
00:30:45,446 --> 00:30:47,486
Love me or hate me,
this is who I am.


634
00:30:47,486 --> 00:30:49,476
Now, this issue was significant


